sequenceDiagram
    participant CLI
    participant Config as ScenarioConfig
    participant Facies as FaciesGenerator
    participant Truth as TruthGenerator
    participant Forward as ForwardLogModel
    participant Realism as RealismEnhancer
    participant Constraints
    participant Artifacts
    participant Export

    CLI->>Config: load + validate YAML
    Config->>Facies: generate depth intervals
    Facies->>Truth: generate Vsh/PHI/Sw/fluid
    Truth->>Forward: calculate base curves
    Forward->>Realism: enhance curve texture
    Realism->>Constraints: enforce physical consistency
    Constraints->>Artifacts: apply noise/washout/gaps/spikes
    Artifacts->>Export: export LAS/truth/manifest/preview
